{"tid":350733,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"【新手／愛情／少糖】我隔離女同學係我女神","createTime":"2017-08-07T12:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T16:29:48.000Z","uid":134170,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"86fb5ae77458b2655b7cb98652e457065e6ca600","tid":350733,"uid":134170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T12:51:33.000Z","msg":"「早晨，我叫莊清源。」我心入面係到諗，就咁介紹自己個名會唔會太簡單？<br />\n<br />\n「你好呀，我叫陳泳彤。」佢露出嗰個笑容真係世界級，簡單啲講就係好親切。<br />\n<br />\n我地相識發生係八秒之內，而我地既關係斷斷續續維持左八年。<br />\n<br />\n「你讀書好叻架？」佢咁樣問我有啲反應唔切。<br />\n<br />\n「其實都係負負碌碌先升到上黎架咋！」係佢面前我又唔想認叻，唯有答個係人都用過既答案。<br />\n<br />\n「你都唔差呀，唔係我都冇機會同你一班！」突然靈機一觸就講左呢句。<br />\n<br />\n「哈哈！」雖然佢只係笑左一笑，但我都已經好滿足。<br />\n<br />\n點解佢會問我呢個問題？因為我係由Ｃ班升上黎Ａ班。<br />\n<br />\n正因為我係Ｃ班升上黎，我英文堂係要去同第二班上，類似係特別班咁。<br />\n<br />\n經過第一堂英文堂既洗禮後，我即刻同呀彤訴苦！<br />\n<br />\n「英文堂，兩個字，好悶！」我望住佢講左呢八個字。<br />\n<br />\n「拿，我就講左八個字，不如你比番八個號碼我啦！」我真係單刀直入問佢拎電話！<br />\n<br />\n「下？」<br />\n<br />\n「你想要我電話號碼做咩呀？」佢充滿疑惑咁問我。<br />\n<br />\n「有左你電話號碼，我地咪可以ＳＭＳ囉！」<br />\n<br />\n「你每上一堂英文堂我就比一個數字你，咁你上堂會唔會開心啲呀？」<br />\n<br />\n為左得到佢既電話號碼，我諗都唔諗就答：「好，一言為定！」我心諗，一星期四堂英文堂，兩個禮拜就拎到，完全冇難度。<br />\n<br />\n為左得到佢既電話號碼，我每日都好期待英文堂，我呢一刻最想就係一日上八堂英文堂！<br />\n<br />\n利伸：各位巴絲手下留情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4d1d65ce40d9d8b96676d7f47340c08233b054","tid":350733,"uid":91733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:03:45.000Z","msg":"加油 快啲出"},{"pid":"a534ee614fcce46a07c5214df8f479c46c7b77db","tid":350733,"uid":123150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:04:54.000Z","msg":"期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca3a5d0fd5fdbecb2083d96cc362c1f7bbbab7b","tid":350733,"uid":24387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f63e1ed60c6454146603fa69ef6e388cc27b74","tid":350733,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T07:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c1d0f6c6930cb0346d6413f9cd454bdde7a768","tid":350733,"uid":134170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:23:30.000Z","msg":"12:45，鐘聲準時響起，迎接我人生嘅第一次，因為中二先可以出去食。<br />\n<br />\n不過我識左呀彤之後，我寧願留返係學校食，起碼可以多啲時間了解佢。<br />\n<br />\n「阿源，冇咗我係咪好唔習慣呢？」呀峰用佢果把低沉嘅聲同我講，我忍唔住打咗個冷震。<br />\n<br />\n「係呀，真係悶到嘔電！」把口雖然係咁講，但其實我心裏面喺度諗：「我開心都嚟唔切啦！」<br />\n<br />\n講起呀峰呢個人，我小學識佢，佢住我隔離，平時最鍾意叫我去佢屋企入房扮溫書實際上入房打機。<br />\n<br />\n「唔係喎！我見你同隔離個女仔好好傾喎！」佢奸笑咁望住我。<br />\n<br />\n「Er...係呀，我今日新識嘅同學。」嗰種感覺就好似你偷偷地打機比阿媽發現左一樣！<br />\n<br />\n「咁你又識唔識到新朋友啊？」我問。<br />\n<br />\n「黎黎去去都係嗰班架啦！」<br />\n<br />\n「不過今年上堂冇得用紙仔騷擾你有啲唔習慣咁囉！」佢答。<br />\n<br />\n我哋同時間抬頭望住大家，無聲仿有聲。<br />\n<br />\n返到班房，發現張凳有張紙仔喺度。<br />\n<br />\n原來上面寫住Kathy Chan，原來呀彤想話俾我知佢英文名，趁佢未返嚟，我係張紙仔嘅背面寫住Charlie Chong再放返落佢張凳。"},{"pid":"420bee534bd2cc09e3dc04b66d1be9de55f980d2","tid":350733,"uid":134170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:26:09.000Z","msg":"好開心有人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13eb53375c95dcbb377fb3265fc8dd3b424c60ee","tid":350733,"uid":123150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:36:19.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ade70d5c0781e6cb7c292d76fe3a20c58e126c7","tid":350733,"uid":134170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:15:06.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲想繼續睇落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ca3a6fe7030e8d27a947530c687421e85a1c4f","tid":350733,"uid":134170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:43:34.000Z","msg":"我次次上完英文堂就係問佢拎一個號碼，將佢收埋係銀包，因為我驚自己太大意會整唔見。<br />\n<br />\n番到屋企第一件事係爬上床將佢掛係窗邊，因為我驚會調亂左次序。<br />\n<br />\n兩個星期既校園生活令佢慢慢融入左係我既生活入面。<br />\n<br />\n「Ｋａｔｈｙ，最後一個號碼係時候交出黎喇！」<br />\n<br />\n「拿！唔好整唔見呀，唔係既話你就搵唔到我架喇！」<br />\n<br />\n「我唔會搵唔到你既，我地一齊讀書架嘛。」<br />\n<br />\n「咁如果有一日我轉左電話號碼呢？」<br />\n<br />\n「咁你打比我同我講番咪得囉，我廿四小時都聽電腦架！」<br />\n<br />\n「哈哈！」<br />\n<br />\n望住佢甜笑住咁遞張紙過黎，再望住上面既一個數字，再諗起佢第一次笑個樣。<br />\n<br />\n我個心真係甜到就黎漏出黎！<br />\n<br />\n番到屋企第一時間掛起張紙仔先，之後就同佢ＳＭＳ！<br />\n<br />\n「我係廿四小時服務專線，轉電話號碼記得打過黎！」我望住手機，緊張又興奮咁打呢兩句。<br />\n<br />\n「點呀你！」<br />\n<br />\n望到呢句，我心諗：「大獲！未問佢咩台！」<br />\n<br />\n「係呢你係咪人仔台架？」我好希望佢答係，因為唔洗收錢。<br />\n<br />\n「係呀，你都應該係啦！」<br />\n<br />\n我望住窗口掛住呢八張紙仔，再望住手機。<br />\n<br />\n我同自己講：「我一定要同佢拍拖，拍一世拖！」"},{"pid":"e31e4cc6af1c0572eaaca2356eb8927d02ac5244","tid":350733,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T15:13:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c658f070d2c487e8317f68af9b10edefd49e5db","tid":350733,"uid":134170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T16:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝幫手推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230353b5e7d3478d647317ecaf13bcc4e2d7e02a","tid":350733,"uid":4930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T17:58:09.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691c889954361d81723bc4faa7f250c049fae73c","tid":350733,"uid":134170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T15:17:48.000Z","msg":"好景不會每日常在。<br />\n<br />\n今次既調位對我黎係一個打擊，望住Ｋａｔｈｙ同左第二個男同學坐，心中有無數既失望，但我唔可以講出口。<br />\n<br />\n「你唔係好多野講架咩？」一把囂張既聲音係耳邊傳黎。<br />\n<br />\n我眼角望左佢一眼，邊有人係人唔開心仲講風涼說話架！<br />\n<br />\n「陳思妍，你可唔可以收下把聲。」我答。<br />\n<br />\n陳思妍呢個人，簡單啲去講佢係個咩人，心腸惡毒既女人一個。<br />\n<br />\n望住Ｋａｔｈｙ同隔離男仔咁好傾，先知原來佢原來唔係對我有好感，只不過有個人可以幫佢解悶。<br />\n<br />\n慢慢我地變到冇咩話題，ＳＭＳ都愈覆愈慢，直至我諗唔到話題，我冇再覆佢，只係得閒會傾兩句。<br />\n<br />\n因為我發覺自己係佢心目中係可有可無。<br />\n<br />\n我每日番屋企第一樣野依然係跑上床，望住果八張紙仔。<br />\n<br />\n隨住日子過去，由開學到考中期試，都係渾渾噩噩咁過。<br />\n<br />\n「你數學幾多分呀？」陳思妍捽住我個頭講<br />\n<br />\n隔離又傳黎呢把黑人憎既聲！<br />\n<br />\n「唔合格呀，你可唔可以收下把聲？」<br />\n<br />\n走廊傳黎放學既鐘聲。<br />\n<br />\n「呀源哥仔，今晚記得黎踢波呀，差你一個咋！」呀峰搭住我膊頭笑笑口咁講。<br />\n<br />\n「得啦，唔好又唔帶波呀！！」我答。<br />\n<br />\n佢每次叫我踢波就話差一個，但係每次都多過七個人踢。<br />\n<br />\n望住佢既背影，有一種好溫暖既感覺。"},{"pid":"5112ac4245e6b3927b0d0f67a698c074abd21526","tid":350733,"uid":135188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續出"},{"pid":"125986de02dced0e8f45cb079cc7374206993361","tid":350733,"uid":134170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:21:20.000Z","msg":"小弟岩岩分手 希望多啲人睇<br />\n當係陪下我渡過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38e5761c7d885bdbfc033f1b0d784dde9c4ee48","tid":350733,"uid":13721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T20:20:49.000Z","msg":"我就係想睇呢啲喇<br />\n快手快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680c791aded66cdea6282a5b587647fcecbfd098","tid":350733,"uid":42759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T10:19:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我就係想睇呢啲喇<br />\n快手快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今晚出兩篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9e68958f348446045cab79c5558221637990c7","tid":350733,"uid":49483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T10:23:57.000Z","msg":"做乜忽然間直線插水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5ac5b03581b621a9e3252c87bec7f3b6f433d4","tid":350733,"uid":123150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T10:46:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7cd2b334ff0f370f3b93ff0407186a0d54cad325","tid":350733,"uid":56320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T10:47:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2879de3ede235b1fe069bbc563c38162ac9260","tid":350733,"uid":134170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:32:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我就係想睇呢啲喇<br />\n快手快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89117b46c28e338292419152014f059ff816270","tid":350733,"uid":134170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:33:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我就係想睇呢啲喇<br />\n快手快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今晚出兩篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今晚有一篇，頂住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e04b7bf56042fd21a45086bebd62e160ac71e8","tid":350733,"uid":132544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:15:04.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"2a4366ca139d8a2d284d30bcc79f766cb3220101","tid":350733,"uid":135188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:19:56.000Z","msg":"等緊文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}